  m_text: Each Level introduces a new mechanic. In this Level You will be learning
    about Wall Jumping and Sliding. To perform a Wall jump demonstated in the image
    above you must Jump onto the wall, once the camera has finished rotating hit
    the jump button again to jump off the wall onto another wall or onto the floor.
    You can only wall jump off certain walls as displayed in the diagram above.
